uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66b01fbe04cc1d75d48ba0759abe94e79c7301d8","tid":2099363,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"熱狗不嬲on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"港父人話都敢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a514d9e974dd01cfaf9d31152c98c3b560202689","tid":2099363,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd4a58c54b29873da12baa483e08c552ed75994d","tid":2099363,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba457506afdd5f0b6315e55071d334efc836eebe","tid":2099363,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5e651f891ff3554de32c342ca7a9f0c98c4f91e","tid":2099363,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"鐵膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200608/346734740470108160.jpeg/_3DK77Bf73fFiIGIqPieRZT6EpB1C4IKcnfWBHJ31gQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200608%2F346734740470108160.jpeg%2F_3DK77Bf73fFiIGIqPieRZT6EpB1C4IKcnfWBHJ31gQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b49130f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200608/346734746065309696.jpeg/hNGZ9vdTqzs3lSMXdg2i5A1WH7yHF_Ce4oHzaeKB82k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200608%2F346734746065309696.jpeg%2FhNGZ9vdTqzs3lSMXdg2i5A1WH7yHF_Ce4oHzaeKB82k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8980f259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200608/346734749064237056.jpeg/_hCm7BW3G_KMn_n43EpYAgQYF_5O4z3jsUdR_rFHUf4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200608%2F346734749064237056.jpeg%2F_hCm7BW3G_KMn_n43EpYAgQYF_5O4z3jsUdR_rFHUf4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2dc170d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n於1921年開始投入服務的313號車卡，本為三等客運車卡，至1980年代初九廣鐵路全線電氣化後，313號車卡亦正式退役。過去313號車卡曾被放在尖沙咀科學館公園展出，後因公園用地需興建歷史博物館，車卡被運到茶果嶺路邊「自生自滅」近十年。數年前政府終耗資600萬元修復、修理及裝置313號歷史車卡，工程已於去年完成，去年除夕夜亦有運輸車輛在鐵路博物館一帶展開運送測試，惟由於當時運送的貨車太長，數月以來未有開始正式運送火車卡。<br />\n<br />\n近日有市民目擊313號車卡在深夜運送到香港鐵路博物館。記者今日到博物館時，只見313號車卡已安裝在最接近戶外展區入口位置，並已與其他車卡連結起來。惟因新冠肺炎疫情關係，現時戶外展區的火車卡都不作開放，參觀者不能走入車廂，只能在路軌位置拍照，連日下雨之下，亦未見有人前來拍攝。據博物館職員指，313號車卡約於上月29日完成裝嵌，數天以來不時有鐵道迷者前來參觀，但近日天氣情況惡劣，遊人也相應減少。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"多得佢<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>香港鐵路博物館暫時關閉<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  康樂及文化事務署今日（七月七日）宣布，因應其中一宗最新2019冠狀病毒病確診個案，為審慎起見，香港鐵路博物館明日（七月八日）暫時關閉一天，以便進行徹底清潔及消毒。<br />\n<br />\n  香港鐵路博物館位於大埔大埔墟崇德街十三號。如有查詢，可致電二六五三 三四五五與該館聯絡。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月7日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間19時35分</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:36:57.000Z","msg":"屌你隻IT狗周圍走,好心拎條狗帶鎖起佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f337aced6dbdf36eb7c27a0d712eca210340fe62","tid":2099363,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91de8d26b391f9577f29c382521b7cf848b80f5a","tid":2099363,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:39:07.000Z","msg":"樓主狙擊夠熱血未 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><